[We are very grateful to Dr Berger for the epidemiological data. Some
of the statements -- e.g. the alleged linkage between urbanization and
the observed Q fever peaks during spring to summer -- might need
clarification (rural vacations of city dwellers?). More information on
animal vaccines, as requested in the RFI, will be helpful. - Mod.AS]
